Messages
--------
- chilly...                       on game start
- smells tasty...                 when smelled new mob
- should check that out...        when moving toward smelled mob
- ouch!                           when getting hit
- ow!                             when getting hit
- uhg                             on death
- *slurp*                         when drinking blood
- need blood...                   when thirsty
- *hiss* *click*                  when locking/cursing door
- *clink*                         when dropping gold

